originalText.text:
Dr. Becker is my OB and I can’t begin to explain how amazing she is. She truly cares about her patients and will go above and beyond for you. She is trustworthy, personable and one of the kindest people I’ve ever met. You can tell she truly loves what she does. She’s a breath of fresh air. She made my experience amazing!!

The medical assistants at the office are very kind as well. The office can get busy sometimes but trust me she is worth waiting for. You’re in great hands with her. Can’t recommend her enough. Thank you Dr. Becker!!!

originalText.text: Dr. Becker is an angel doctor! I was supposed to have a different doctor deliver my baby, but he was a no-show. Dr Becker stepped in and I’m so thrilled that she had. This was the best thing that could have happened to me. She was extraordinary throughout the delivery, she stitched me up so well, & I healed beautifully. I couldn’t be more pleased with her professionalism, communication skills, confidence, and empathy. She’s the ideal OBGYN, so brilliant & so vibrant, and I really couldn’t put my trust in anyone else. Going to see her is such a joy. Five stars all day.

originalText.text: I had been seeing Dr. Becker through out my pregnancy and can't say enough how wonderful she was through out the process. She has a great, laid back demeanor that I found so comforting. I had some complications and things didn't go as expected with my delivery and recovery, however Dr. Becker was there for me every step of the way and I can't imagine not having her on our "team." Truly an amazing doctor and person! She is personable and kind and someone you want by your side every step of the way.
